  "title": "Managing Director – Strategy",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><p>•       Design\nand implement strategic business plans that expand company’s global client base\nand future growth potentials</p><p>•       Interpret\nand analyse client requirements into business model architecture.</p><p>•       Devise\ninnovative and unconventional solutions to bridge customer demands and\nquantitative-based product designs. </p><p>•       Identify\nglobal new markets in terms of geographic access and multi-lingual marketing,\nwith a focus in building open communities from ground-up.</p><p>•       Build\nand promote strong, long-lasting relationships with global partners including\nfinancial institutions, fintech companies, and crypto firms.</p><p>•       Prepared\nfor challenges of a 24/7 market which may at times require odd-hours or weekend\ncommitments.         </p><p>Skills & Experience Required:</p><p>•       Minimum\ndegree requirement: Bachelor’s degree & above, with managerial disciplines\nsuch as Finance, Management or related fields. An MBA degree is preferred.</p><p>•       Minimum\n15 years of prior experience in financial industry or FinTech start-up, with\nteam management experience. Proven global mobility record in different\ngeographic locations is a plus.</p><p>•       Excellent\nwritten and spoken communication skills in English is a must. Mandarin is a\nbonus, for effectively communication both internally and with all levels of\nclients’ organization</p><p>•       Advanced\nknowledge of business management, strategic planning, and online business users\ngrowth</p><p>•       Advanced\nknowledge of financial risk management, with a focus in large financial\ninstitutions or multinational conglomerates</p><p>•       Exceptional\nproject management and organisation skills, excellent interpersonal skills,\nstrong problem-solving skills and sense of ownership</p><p>•       Proven\nability to prioritize workload, make systematic and logical decisions under\npressure</p><p>•       Possess\nan entrepreneurial ‘can do’ mindset, able to work in a start-up environment</p><p>•       Team\nplayer with high degree of integrity. </p><p>We pride ourselves on being a flat and\nagile organization a strong emphasis on team excellence while providing ample\nspace for individual growth and development. \nWe value the intellectual curiosity and critical reasoning from each\nmember of our multi-disciplinary team.</p>",
